**window.scrollTO  --> it is used to set the tart positon in px , 
**meanining from initilal position to destination point
**vertical movement  |
                     |
                     V

______________________________________________________

window.scrollTo(0,200);   //from start  to 200px down

       //or

window.scrollTo(0,600);   //from start  to 600px down

______________________________________________________



